transcript.text: Hello, welcome to on print shop.
In this video we will see the new feature My Account Links Management control for Site Admin which we have added in version 7.1 earlier.
We do not have any control on the links of My account.
Either we can disable the entire link or can show all links.
But in new version Site Admin, either Super Admin or Corporate Admin can manage the links.
Go to Corporate under the Corporate management, click on Action button and then select Edit.
Scroll down the page under Content settings we see a new option for My account links here If we select default then all default link are shown in My account button.
If we select none and save the setting, refresh the page on Corporate front store.
We will see that My account link will disappear.
If we select custom then from the list we need to check the link which we want Corporate front store.
Click on Save to save the changes.
Refresh the page on corporate front store side.
We will see only that link which we have checked from the admin.
Thank you for watching this video.
For more help, please send us an e-mail at support at on printshop.com.
